Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.61,0:01:48.70,*Default1,46,0000,0000,0000,,初花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.46,*Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我已經很久沒注意過季節的替換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.83,*Default5,48,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}白杉站...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.37,*Default5,49,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}白杉站...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.95,*Default5,50,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}終點站, 若瀬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:21.46,*Default5,51,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}請稍後, 特級列車將於...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.79,0:02:32.59,*Default5,52,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}現在是春天這個事實, 到底能有多大的意義呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.91,*Default5,53,0000,0000,0000,,我...已經有了喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.19,0:03:06.43,*Default5,54,0000,0000,0000,,啊...這樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.27,*Default5,55,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}津花站 ,津花站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.27,0:03:49.07,*Default5,56,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}{\a6}電車停穩前請耐心等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.78,*Default5,57,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 我要下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.17,*Default5,58,0000,0000,0000,,啊...借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.35,*Default5,59,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.63,*Default5,60,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 同學!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.56,*Default5,61,0000,0000,0000,,請問?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.33,*Default5,62,0000,0000,0000,,喔...這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.75,0:05:04.04,*Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,討厭...我竟然發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.94,*Default5,64,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.07,*Default5,65,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.99,0:05:27.53,*Default5,66,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.69,*Default5,67,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次的相親派對就說到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.71,*Default5,68,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有其他問題的話, 我想就到此結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.40,*Default5,69,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.44,*Default5,70,0000,0000,0000,,小田切?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.88,0:05:38.79,*Default5,71,0000,0000,0000,,這次雖然是限25歲以上35歲以下會員參加的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.36,*Default5,72,0000,0000,0000,,但如果將會員條件降到15歲或17歲左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.52,*Default5,73,0000,0000,0000,,特別是女性會員...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.92,*Default5,74,0000,0000,0000,,到此結束!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.02,*Default5,75,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:49.20,*Default5,76,0000,0000,0000,,走 去吃飯吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.40,*Default5,77,0000,0000,0000,,去哪吃呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.08,*Default5,78,0000,0000,0000,,轉角處不是新開一家餐廳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.37,*Default5,79,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.16,*Default5,80,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.12,*Default5,81,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.96,*Default5,82,0000,0000,0000,,你今天在這裡整理會員資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:09.89,*Default5,83,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.63,*Default5,84,0000,0000,0000,,你那張臉! 那味道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.36,*Default5,85,0000,0000,0000,,能出去見人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.13,*Default5,86,0000,0000,0000,,應該確實有這種需要才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.58,*Default5,87,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:28.08,*Default5,88,0000,0000,0000,,根據經驗,像我這種年紀也只能\N透過非官方形式認識10幾歲的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.99,*Default5,89,0000,0000,0000,,你的需求嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.33,0:06:35.15,*Default5,90,0000,0000,0000,,難道就沒有能認識女高中生的機會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.01,*Default5,91,0000,0000,0000,,夠了, 工作吧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.83,*Default5,92,0000,0000,0000,,我回來...了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.31,*Default5,93,0000,0000,0000,,這事我可沒聽說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.97,*Default5,94,0000,0000,0000,,總之, 明天晚上就開始要和七夏一起住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.98,*Default5,95,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.31,*Default5,96,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這麼突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.62,*Default5,97,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓你看看七夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.01,*Default5,98,0000,0000,0000,,已經不記得了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.01,0:07:44.76,*Default5,99,0000,0000,0000,,我記得的...記是記得, 長相已經忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.28,*Default5,100,0000,0000,0000,,現在讀高一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.81,*Default5,101,0000,0000,0000,,十五歲哦! 很可愛的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.05,0:07:53.45,*Default5,102,0000,0000,0000,,從遠地上學, 別人不也都這樣嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.20,*Default5,103,0000,0000,0000,,原來兩個小時的路程一個小時就夠了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.80,*Default5,104,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子, 讓她住進來也算自然的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.90,*Default5,105,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是因為你被情人拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.64,*Default5,106,0000,0000,0000,,而想和老媽復合吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.58,*Default5,107,0000,0000,0000,,那...那怎麼可能嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.11,*Default5,108,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.11,0:08:09.95,*Default5,109,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.95,0:08:10.86,*Default5,110,0000,0000,0000,,她是我女兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.80,*Default5,111,0000,0000,0000,,親骨肉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.93,*Default5,112,0000,0000,0000,,也是你的妹妹吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.59,*Default5,113,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}跟老爸一起生活的悠閒感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.40,*Default5,114,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}有時會讓我忘記一些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:34.12,*Default5,115,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我還有母親和一位小我十二歲的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.00,*Default5,116,0000,0000,0000,,請介紹給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.27,*Default5,117,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在想什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.27,0:08:52.53,*Default5,118,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都不告訴我, 這麼重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.54,*Default5,119,0000,0000,0000,,不是想瞞你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.77,*Default5,120,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我也一樣不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.01,*Default5,121,0000,0000,0000,,我父母離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.03,*Default5,122,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和我母親見過幾次面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.27,*Default5,123,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有見過妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.62,*Default5,124,0000,0000,0000,,有客人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.73,*Default5,125,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓您久等...了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.92,*Default5,126,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.63,*Default5,127,0000,0000,0000,,妳想找什麼樣的對象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.48,*Default5,128,0000,0000,0000,,先別生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.98,*Default5,129,0000,0000,0000,,上班時間來找你, 我知道不對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.88,0:09:40.36,*Default5,130,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.28,*Default5,131,0000,0000,0000,,反正是午休時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.02,*Default5,132,0000,0000,0000,,房間的鑰匙, 我想請你還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:51.51,*Default5,133,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得...趁白天來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.93,*Default5,134,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.74,0:10:07.77,*Default5,135,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.83,*Default5,136,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.41,*Default5,137,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是爽快呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.00,*Default5,138,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.28,*Default5,139,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.36,*Default5,140,0000,0000,0000,,你回答得還真簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.71,*Default5,141,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.71,0:10:32.87,*Default5,142,0000,0000,0000,,唉, 原來我就只有這麼一點份量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.78,0:10:42.74,*Default5,143,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎你...有從心裡真正喜歡過誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.10,0:11:06.86,*Default5,144,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎你...有從心裡真正喜歡過誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.71,*Default5,145,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那麼...我該怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.78,*Default5,146,0000,0000,0000,,因為派對中會穿插三次活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.78,0:11:24.70,*Default5,147,0000,0000,0000,,料理希望能夠配合時間分別送上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.23,*Default5,148,0000,0000,0000,,然後是關於音響設備的問題...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.31,*Default5,149,0000,0000,0000,,那麼, 請您多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.54,*Default5,150,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.11,*Default5,151,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.76,*Default5,152,0000,0000,0000,,這個, 是遊樂場的, 不嫌棄的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.98,0:11:43.01,*Default5,153,0000,0000,0000,,啊...不好意思, 那就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.72,0:11:50.55,*Default5,154,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}對說有了其他喜歡的男人的女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.50,*Default5,155,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我還能說什麼 做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.91,*Default5,156,0000,0000,0000,,風景真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.48,*Default5,157,0000,0000,0000,,對單身漢來說卻是個傷心地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.27,*Default5,158,0000,0000,0000,,還是分手了呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.68,*Default5,159,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.73,*Default5,160,0000,0000,0000,,你還真冷靜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.56,*Default5,161,0000,0000,0000,,她說就是討厭這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.79,*Default5,162,0000,0000,0000,,這個...送給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.29,*Default5,163,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.92,*Default5,164,0000,0000,0000,,去約那個分手的女孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.80,*Default5,165,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能復合唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:33.58,*Default5,166,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要跟她復合了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.47,*Default5,167,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.41,0:12:56.52,*Default5,168,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.30,*Default5,169,0000,0000,0000,,那個...你不記得了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.17,*Default5,170,0000,0000,0000,,昨天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.16,*Default5,171,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 我記得!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.35,*Default5,172,0000,0000,0000,,我記得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.80,*Default5,173,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.67,*Default5,174,0000,0000,0000,,真是個壞傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.00,*Default5,175,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跟女高中生搭訕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.50,*Default5,176,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.39,*Default5,177,0000,0000,0000,,昨天太感謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.73,*Default5,178,0000,0000,0000,,那...不好意思打擾你們約會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.03,*Default5,179,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.31,*Default5,180,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.60,*Default5,181,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.33,*Default5,182,0000,0000,0000,,我說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.79,*Default5,183,0000,0000,0000,,是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.10,*Default5,184,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.23,*Default5,185,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.71,*Default5,186,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.15,*Default5,187,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.27,*Default5,188,0000,0000,0000,,太好了, 其實我在等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.84,*Default5,189,0000,0000,0000,,但來得太早了, 正不知道要怎麼打發時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.13,*Default5,190,0000,0000,0000,,等人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.30,*Default5,191,0000,0000,0000,,嗯! 等我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.37,*Default5,192,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 我們要坐什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.80,*Default5,193,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.22,*Default5,194,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.25,*Default5,195,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.29,*Default5,196,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.29,*Default5,197,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.45,*Default5,198,0000,0000,0000,,哇! 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.67,*Default5,199,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.49,*Default5,200,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起很無聊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.71,*Default5,201,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.41,*Default5,202,0000,0000,0000,,你應該有男朋友吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.40,*Default5,203,0000,0000,0000,,我...剛剛失戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.00,*Default5,204,0000,0000,0000,,哇! 好漂亮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.58,*Default5,205,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.68,*Default5,206,0000,0000,0000,,是在初中的畢業典禮得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.94,*Default5,207,0000,0000,0000,,從喜歡的人那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.91,*Default5,208,0000,0000,0000,,但是...卻不是第二顆鈕扣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.91,*Default5,209,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(注:在日本,在畢業典禮上,將制服的第二顆鈕扣\N送給喜歡的女孩是一種傳統, 也是表白)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.80,*Default5,210,0000,0000,0000,,是從初一就喜歡上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.73,*Default5,211,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不覺得他有多帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.42,*Default5,212,0000,0000,0000,,但卻非常地喜歡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.21,*Default5,213,0000,0000,0000,,終於鼓起勇氣向他告白了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.53,*Default5,214,0000,0000,0000,,但他卻說正在和學妹交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.40,*Default5,215,0000,0000,0000,,這些事我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.55,*Default5,216,0000,0000,0000,,明明打開窗戶就能把鈕扣丟下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.86,*Default5,217,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.49,*Default5,218,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼丟下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.95,*Default5,219,0000,0000,0000,,妳還喜歡他吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.81,*Default5,220,0000,0000,0000,,是的話, 就別說什麼丟下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.46,*Default5,221,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.42,*Default5,222,0000,0000,0000,,我必須忘了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.14,*Default5,223,0000,0000,0000,,他已經跟別人交往了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.98,*Default5,224,0000,0000,0000,,連高中也在不同的地方讀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.77,*Default5,225,0000,0000,0000,,已經見不到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.85,*Default5,226,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.88,*Default5,227,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你那麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.67,*Default5,228,0000,0000,0000,,真坦率啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.76,*Default5,229,0000,0000,0000,,妳又是為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.63,0:17:38.70,*Default5,230,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能那麼坦率地喜歡一個人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.26,*Default5,231,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.89,*Default5,232,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛被人甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.02,*Default5,233,0000,0000,0000,,但和你就完全不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.71,*Default5,234,0000,0000,0000,,我給別人的感覺是很冷淡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:18:05.18,*Default5,235,0000,0000,0000,,甚至...都不知道自己是不是真的喜歡她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.71,*Default5,236,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.15,*Default5,237,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:16.18,*Default5,238,0000,0000,0000,,妳心裡的那份情感...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.10,*Default5,239,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.59,*Default5,240,0000,0000,0000,,啊...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.30,*Default5,241,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.81,*Default5,242,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.44,*Default5,243,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.95,*Default5,244,0000,0000,0000,,我失戀以後每天都低著頭走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.17,0:19:40.28,*Default5,245,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道櫻花已經開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.88,*Default5,246,0000,0000,0000,,昨天, 你在車站叫住我的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.65,*Default5,247,0000,0000,0000,,才第一次注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.60,*Default5,248,0000,0000,0000,,真的好意外!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.49,*Default5,249,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣像雪花一樣飄下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.46,*Default5,250,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間都不知道自己身處何處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.52,*Default5,251,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我也是...這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.82,*Default5,252,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}這裡...到底是哪裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.67,*Default5,253,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一直待在這裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.95,*Default5,254,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是不被允許的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.84,*Default5,255,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.74,*Default5,256,0000,0000,0000,,彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.91,*Default5,257,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.32,*Default5,258,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.87,*Default5,259,0000,0000,0000,,那 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.78,*Default5,260,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.70,*Default5,261,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀呀! 抱歉抱歉, 我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.99,*Default5,262,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.99,*Default5,263,0000,0000,0000,,老爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.62,*Default5,264,0000,0000,0000,,嘿?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.78,*Default5,265,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼? 耕四郎也來了呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.11,*Default5,266,0000,0000,0000,,你們兄妹倆真是好久不見了呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.16,*Default5,267,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆一見面就認出來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.93,0:21:10.04,*Default5,268,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 你們兩人! 來, 走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.73,*Default5,269,0000,0000,0000,,等...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.71,*Default5,270,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐去哪吃好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.92,*Default5,271,0000,0000,0000,,七夏, 妳想吃什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.48,*Default5,272,0000,0000,0000,,等...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.72,0:21:21.88,*Default5,273,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.34,*Default5,274,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.33,*Default5,275,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.45,*Default5,276,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.82,0:21:37.10,*Default5,277,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一個妹妹
